{"tid":806595,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"新手 相機 60M 100M位元率一問","createTime":"2018-09-04T20:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T23:34:09.000Z","uid":167326,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7e5c2f7ded16aa279f3ae38005cf8329ca2c5176","tid":806595,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T20:55:00.000Z","msg":"相機錄片設定上有好多種唔同嘅位元率揀<br />\n我上網搵左好耐資料 知道左係關於資料嘅傳輸。 比如打機直播 高位元率 畫質會清啲傳輸到更大流量影片<br />\n<br />\n但相機嘅運作係點？係傳輸落張卡嘅速度？我諗唔明。 <br />\n<br />\n總括黎講我拍4K 25p 100M 同拍4K 25p 60M ，100M嘅畫質會靚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"2036b7cda55a33a698188098313f17a359aa1536","tid":806595,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:10:57.000Z","msg":"有冇人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b69412d5d0b5892177922253127c368c7ad6d71","tid":806595,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:16:07.000Z","msg":"MB/s"},{"pid":"e5b4e80211bbe7909a6fa978cf0f48713eca7f2f","tid":806595,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:17:08.000Z","msg":"10 bit color"},{"pid":"f71a119a9cff65e22be1dcb3c741b9e0e0599f20","tid":806595,"uid":34589,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:07:06.000Z","msg":"拍片會壓縮，無壓縮嗰File Size會大到你會懷疑人生。<br />\nMbps 每秒資料量，包括左pixels、n-bit color等等。<br />\n100Mbps相比起60Mbps會低啲壓縮，一般資料量越大後製程度可以越大，調色嗰陣出色塊機會會降低、保留較多暗位嘅細節等等等。至於會唔會清晰啲喺會的，不過應該100Mbps同60Mbps感覺肉眼就咁睇無幾大分別，可以google下5Mbps vs 50Mbps。<br />\n不過當然越大Mbps檔案會越大啦。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 平時拍開RAW Video<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61dd0339fcc94387619c96af63a7014a0cf797f1","tid":806595,"uid":93358,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:26:45.000Z","msg":"相機拍片100Mbps係講拍片時每秒記錄低嘅data有幾多。<br />\n<br />\n*注意 細楷b=bit，大楷B=Byte<br />\n1Byte=8bit<br />\n所以100Mbps其實係～12.5MB/s<br />\n<br />\neg:<br />\n4k25p 100Mbps/s，除開1秒25格，<br />\n即係每frame大概4Mb(0.5MB)到。<br />\n4k25p 60MB/s-&gt; 每frame大概2.4Mb(0.3MB)。<br />\n<br />\n100Mbps比60Mbps會細緻d，顏色都會準dd。<br />\n<br />\n色域/顏色/光暗過渡就睇10bit/8bit多d<br />\n10bit會好過8bit好多"},{"pid":"a596c82c9e533c9525ab975474472fd171cd84d2","tid":806595,"uid":167326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:53:24.000Z","msg":"跪地多謝指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e9bacf5b52a333678cb454431f2401cfcb6a79","tid":806595,"uid":3931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T23:34:09.000Z","msg":"要睇埋compression rate<br />\n畫面取樣sampling<br />\n<br />\nFile size 大唔一定有優勢"}]}